data.description: A dollhouse near downtown Hartselle. This home has character and could be a first time homebuyers dream or a great investment property. This 2 bed, 1 bath has spacious bedrooms with lots of natural light, beautiful hardwood floors, metal roof and a storage building in the backyard. There are a few cosmetic projects you could complete and make it your own. Located off HWY 36, near shopping and convenient to I65. Don't let this one get away. Schedule your showing today! No showings after 5pm.
